descript.abstract:
This text (csv) file contains the location coordinates for all NGEE-Arctic related instrumentation and sampling sites near Barrow, Alaska.  Coordinates are provided in both UTM northing (meters) and easting (meters), and decimal degrees latitude and longtitude.  The datum for which these coordinates was acquired is NAD83, UTM Zone 4North.  &#xD;
&#xD;
This data currently DOES NOT INCLUDE CORE SAMPLE LOCATIONS.  These will be updated and included in spring, 2015.&#xD;
&#xD;
Instrument and sample sites include in this data are:&#xD;
diffusion cells&#xD;
eddy covariance tower&#xD;
frost table transects&#xD;
GPS benchmarks&#xD;
heavometers&#xD;
15n samples&#xD;
soil temperature moisture networks&#xD;
solar power stations&#xD;
snow cameras&#xD;
synoptic water samples&#xD;
thermal profiles including soil pits, precipitation gauges, boreholes, and snow depth gauges&#xD;
tundra tram&#xD;
vegetation and biogeochemistry (BGC)plots&#xD;
wells
